e, [[Douglas Furber]], [[Stephen Fry]] and [[Mike Ockrent]]'''\n| '''''[[Me and My Girl]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n| Barry Harman\n| ''[[Olympus on My Mind]]''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 1988\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[James Lapine]]'''\n| '''''[[Into the Woods]]'' \u2020'''\n|}\n\n===1990s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:98%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#bebebe;\"\n! style=\"width:10%;\"| Year\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Writer\n! style=\"width:60%;\"| Production\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 1990\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Larry Gelbart]]'''\n| '''''[[City of Angels (musical)|City of Angels]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"| 1991\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Marsha Norman]]'''\n| '''''[[The Secret Garden (musical)|The Secret Garden]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n| [[John Weidman]]\n| ''[[Assassins (musical)|Assassins]]''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 1992\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[George C. Wolfe]]'''\n| '''''[[Jelly's Last Jam]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"| 1994\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[James Lapine]]'''\n| '''''[[Passion (musical)|Passion]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n| [[Michael John LaChiusa]]\n| ''[[Hello Again (musical)|Hello Again]]''\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1995\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\"| 1996\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Jonathan Larson]]'''\n| '''''[[Rent (musical)|Rent]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n| [[Graciela Daniele]] and Jim Lewis\n| ''[[Chronicle of a Death Foretold (musical)|Chronicle of a Death Foretold]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| Laurence Klavan\n| ''[[Bed and Sofa]]''\n|-\n| [[Tina Landau]]\n| ''[[Floyd Collins (musical)|Floyd Collins]]''\n|-\n| [[John Weidman]]\n| ''[[Big: the musical]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1997\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 1998\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Terrence McNally]]'''\n| '''''[[Ragtime (musical)|Ragtime]]'' \u2020'''\