icked (musical)|Wicked]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n| [[Tony Kushner]]\n| ''[[Caroline, or Change]]'' \u2021\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" align=\"center\"| 2005\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''Rachel Sheinkin'''\n| '''''[[The 25th Annual Putnam County Spelling Bee]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n| Nell Benjamin and [[Laurence O'Keefe (composer)|Laurence O'Keefe]]\n| ''Cam Jensen''\n|-\n| Kevin Del Aguila\n| ''[[Altar Boyz]]''\n|-\n| [[Mark Harelik]]\n| ''[[The Immigrant (musical)|The Immigrant]]''\n|-\n| [[Eric Idle]]\n| ''[[Spamalot|Monty Python's Spamalot]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| [[Jeffrey Lane]]\n| ''[[Dirty Rotten Scoundrels (musical)|Dirty Rotten Scoundrels]]'' \u2021\n|-\n! rowspan=\"4\" align=\"center\"| 2006\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Bob Martin (comedian)|Bob Martin]] and [[Don McKellar]]'''\n| '''''[[The Drowsy Chaperone]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n| [[Rick Elice]] and [[Marshall Brickman]]\n| ''[[Jersey Boys]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| [[Doug Wright]]\n| ''[[Grey Gardens (musical)|Grey Gardens]]'' \u2021\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" align=\"center\"| 2007\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Rupert Holmes]] and [[Peter Stone]]'''\n| '''''[[Curtains (musical)|Curtains]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n| Scott Brown and [[Anthony King (writer)|Anthony King]]\n| ''[[Gutenberg! The Musical!]]''\n|-\n| [[Julian Fellowes]]\n| ''[[Mary Poppins (musical)|Mary Poppins]]''\n|-\n| [[Heather Hach]]\n| ''[[Legally Blonde (musical)|Legally Blonde]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| [[Steven Sater]]\n| ''[[Spring Awakening (musical)|Spring Awakening]]'' \u2020\n|-\n| [[Alfred Uhry]]\n| ''[[LoveMusik]]''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" align=\"center\"| 2008\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[Douglas Carter Beane]]'''\n| '''''[[Xanadu (musical)|Xanadu]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n| [[Harvey Fierstein]]\n| ''[[A Catered Affair]]''\n|-\n| [[Ben Katchor]]\n| ''The Slug Bearers of Kayrol Island''\n|-\n| Jason Loewith and Joshua Schmidt\n| ''[[Adding Machine (musical)|Adding Machine]]''\n|-\n| [[Stew (musician)|Stew]]\n| ''[[Passing Strange (musical)|Passing Str