rell (author)|John O\u2019Farrell]]\n| ''[[Something Rotten!]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| [[Craig Lucas]]\n| ''[[An American in Paris (film)#Stage adaptations|An American in Paris]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| [[Terrence McNally]]\n| ''[[The Visit (musical)|The Visit]]'' \u2021\n|-\n| Kim Rosenstock, Will Connolly, and Michael Mitnick\n| ''Fly by Night''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"4\" align=\"center\"| 2016\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| '''[[John Caird (director)|John Caird]]'''\n| '''''[[Daddy Long Legs (musical)|Daddy Long Legs]]'''''\n|-\n| [[Michael John LaChiusa]]\n| ''[[First Daughter Suite]]''\n|-\n| [[Jessie Nelson (filmmaker)|Jessie Nelson]]\n| ''[[Waitress (musical)|Waitress]]'' \n|-\n! rowspan=\"6\" |2017\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n|'''[[Irene Sankoff]] and [[David Hein]]'''\n|'''''[[Come from Away]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n|[[Terrence McNally]]\n|[[Anastasia (musical)|''Anastasia'']]\n|-\n|[[Itamar Moses]]\n|[[The Band's Visit (musical)|''The Band's Visit'']] \u2020 \n|-\n|Richard Oberacker and Rob Taylor\n|[[Bandstand (musical)|''Bandstand'']]\n|-\n|Joe Tracz\n|''[[The Lightning Thief (musical)|The Lightning Thief: The Percy Jackson Musical]]''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"5\" |2018\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n|'''[[Tina Fey]]'''\n|'''''[[Mean Girls (musical)|Mean Girls]]'' \u2021'''\n|-\n|[[Kyle Jarrow]]\n|''[[SpongeBob SquarePants (musical)|SpongeBob SquarePants]]'' \u2021\n|-\n|[[Peter Kellogg (writer)|Peter Kellogg]]\n|''[[Desperate Measures (musical)|Desperate Measures]]''\n|-\n|[[Hannah Moscovitch]]\n|''Old Stock: A Refugee Love Story''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"6\" |2019\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n|'''[[Robert Horn (writer)|Robert Horn]]'''\n|'''''[[Tootsie (musical)|Tootsie]]'' \u2020'''\n|-\n|Scott Brown and [[Anthony King (writer)|Anthony King]]\n|''[[Beetlejuice (musical)|Beetlejuice]]'' \u2021\n|-\n|Andrew R. Butler\n|''[[Rags Parkland Sings the Songs of the Future]]''\n|-\n|[[Bob Martin (comedian)|Bob Martin]] and [[Chad Beguelin]]\n|''[[The Prom (musical)|The Prom]]'' \u202